{
  "text": "Fourth, a much reduced or no P600 is observed for syntactic errors in \"Jabberwocky\" sentences, i.e., sentences that include function words/morphemes but cannot be interpreted with respect to world knowledge [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . In such cases, it is difficult to infer plausibly intended meanings because the materials are, by design, devoid of meaning.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "21809369",
